    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/b3b6778505896a08e3b04b847a743d33.avif?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><br>在这款动作冒险游戏中证明自己，一边探索神秘的古文明遗迹，一边迎接紧张刺激的战斗。失落山谷阿克雷亚虽然荒凉破败、杂草丛生，却蕴藏着强大力量。你发现了这片被人遗忘的土地，但却死于非命。时光飞逝，你奇迹般地复活了，然而你付出的代价是：困在了这片土地上。 <br><br>在可靠伙伴博吉的指引下踏上征程，探索高耸入云的宫殿以及失落已久的城市，将这个惨遭毁坏、饱受战争摧残的地方恢复昔日的平静。做好准备！随着秘密的逐渐揭露，你会遇到越来越致命的敌人和愈发凶险的世界，踏上旅程，去体验令人难忘的冒险吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/489e597126b1472b0269b2186ec162c6.webp?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/c54e8d6ce78533ee084da6a1e14ef021.webp?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br>你将踏上令人难忘的旅程，探索阿克雷亚及其远古遗留物背后的故事，了解这个山谷沦为战场与死亡之地背后的来龙去脉。摧毁过去的遗留势力，帮助这个饱受战争摧残的山谷恢复昔日的和平。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/2f981d7b99411df5bdca056afa8fb879.poster.avif?t=1700061034\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/2f981d7b99411df5bdca056afa8fb879.webm?t=1700061034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/2f981d7b99411df5bdca056afa8fb879.mp4?t=1700061034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/e90868661230de86349acef04ff5ac55.webp?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br>变化是旅程的一部分，每一场胜利都会在世界中留下印记。即便你阵亡，时间依然会继续流逝。重游之前的胜利之地，你会感受到世界的变化，不过要小心！你的挑战会原来越艰巨。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/6977ca70476f437e26dbcbc632d67447.webp?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br>战斗非常顺畅，你可以快速反应，精确攻击，在持械近战时预判敌方攻击并瞬间做出对剑反应。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/61af23fb40a448763c6f9f61115724bc.poster.avif?t=1700061034\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/61af23fb40a448763c6f9f61115724bc.webm?t=1700061034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/61af23fb40a448763c6f9f61115724bc.mp4?t=1700061034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/45cf225ef4e135671f7f19ff2479d9df.webp?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br>与这片土地的神王战斗，消灭其残余势力，让这片土地从远古时代的阴影中解放。汲取他们的力量，揭开阿克雷亚的秘密，新领域等待着你的解锁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/f81666aac8fc8e4f05b8cdbeeefe3677.webp?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br>冒险者和博吉各有不同的天赋树。冒险者是一位战士，通过战斗获得经验，而博吉是一位工匠，通过寻找远古传说的碎片增长经验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/7a6b88582e717021d15c35e22649a169.webp?t=1700061034\" width=616 height=27 /></span><br>阿克雷亚的世界五彩缤纷，那里有杂草丛生的城市遗迹，还有冰封的洞穴和蜿蜒的峡谷。你可以探索这个世界中最隐秘的角落，或是找到一些罕见的材料、配方、武器以及传说碎片，每一次冒险都不会空手而归。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/730cf335171fdf78a6acc702075c4d83.poster.avif?t=1700061034\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/730cf335171fdf78a6acc702075c4d83.webm?t=1700061034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621990/extras/730cf335171fdf78a6acc702075c4d83.mp4?t=1700061034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
